(skipme-segments.db) is crowd-sourced community data and is distinct from
the plugin's source code.  It is NOT licensed under the GPL.

The locally-cached data ("Cached Data") is provided solely to supply media
segment timestamps to the Jellyfin media server through this plugin.  By
